Enum Mode backed by u8 has idle be 0; active be 1.

To make modes, giving owned buffer of Mode.
Let modes be owned buffer of 3 Mode filled with Mode.idle.
modes at 1 becomes Mode.active.
Give modes.

To main, giving i32.
Let modes be make modes.
Give 7 when modes at 1 is equal to Mode.active; otherwise 3.
